WEBVTT

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:08.933
Charles!

00:00:09.133 --> 00:00:10.133
You there?

00:00:10.470 --> 00:00:11.266
Our interview

00:00:11.266 --> 00:00:12.600
was set for 10 AM.

00:00:12.733 --> 00:00:13.966
It's already 11 now!

00:00:14.733 --> 00:00:15.400
Charles?

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:16.033
You can't be

00:00:16.033 --> 00:00:17.733
late for the fan meeting!

00:00:17.833 --> 00:00:18.400
Charles!

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:19.000
Are you up?

00:00:19.033 --> 00:00:19.866
Open up!

00:00:19.866 --> 00:00:21.066
Charles, you there?

00:00:21.933 --> 00:00:22.433
Joseph!

00:00:22.433 --> 00:00:23.066
Hey!

00:00:23.066 --> 00:00:23.800
Get up, quick!

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:24.633
Someone's here!

00:00:24.633 --> 00:00:25.300
Get dressed!

00:00:25.300 --> 00:00:26.050
You'll ruin my

00:00:26.050 --> 00:00:26.733
reputation!

00:00:26.733 --> 00:00:27.566
Charles?

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:28.266
Open up!

00:00:28.700 --> 00:00:30.100
Charles, you there?

00:00:36.900 --> 00:00:37.433
Damn,

00:00:37.466 --> 00:00:38.433
my ass...

00:00:40.300 --> 00:00:41.900
Is he not home?

00:00:42.500 --> 00:00:43.433
But his delivery

00:00:43.433 --> 00:00:44.000
is here.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:45.200
Maybe he's not up.

00:00:45.533 --> 00:00:46.200
Charles!

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:47.500
Are you up?

00:00:47.800 --> 00:00:48.433
Go, go!

00:00:49.100 --> 00:00:49.800
Get in, quick!

00:00:50.400 --> 00:00:51.033
Charles?

00:00:51.400 --> 00:00:52.166
I can't get in,

00:00:52.166 --> 00:00:52.966
it's too small.

00:00:53.500 --> 00:00:54.800
That sounds familiar...

00:00:54.800 --> 00:00:55.800
I think I said that

00:00:55.833 --> 00:00:56.800
last night.

00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:02.333
Piss off!

00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:03.833
Is he still sleeping?

00:01:03.866 --> 00:01:04.600
He did look

00:01:04.600 --> 00:01:05.133
a bit off 

00:01:05.166 --> 00:01:06.400
when he went home.

00:01:06.566 --> 00:01:07.766
Wait, did he pass out?

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:09.800
Charles!

00:01:09.933 --> 00:01:11.366
Charles, are you in there?

00:01:11.366 --> 00:01:11.966
Stop.

00:01:11.966 --> 00:01:12.866
Let's break in.

